resources.string: Join in the fight for Democracy today! By simply entering your super government credentials you will officially be entered into the Helldiver intro course and sent an official draft letter within 1 hour. After a quick Helldiver Physical Exam you will earn your cape and be ready to spread Managed Democracy to faraway planets! Be on the right side of history; be a Helldiver.
I am willing to die for Super Earth and am ready to perish in the pursuit of spreading managed democracy to the galaxy
Current orders for Helldivers, join now and support fellow Helldivers in this mission!
